画監督：小野ひろみ","ep":3,"sort":51,"id":1663065,"subject_id":533027,"comment":37,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-01","name":"クライマックスと彼女-クラカノ-","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"「違う、水原はそんなコじゃないよ」\r\n和也はみんなへ涙ながらに訴える。騎士（ナイト）気取りの、“最後の見栄”を張る和也。\r\n木部は和也の胸ぐらを掴んで真偽を問い詰めるが、和也の気持ちは揺るがない。\r\nそんな中、麻美が和也と千鶴にキスを要求する。周囲の視線が集まる中、動揺する和也。一方瑠夏は、かつての麻美との会話を思い出しつつ、自身がどう立ち回るべきか決断を迫られる。このまま黙って成り行きを静観するのか、それとも──。\r\n\r\n脚本：広田光毅\r\n絵コンテ：古賀一臣\r\n演出：中野彰子\r\nキャラクターデザイン監修：平山寛菜\r\n総作画監督：鷲田敏弥、菊地華子","ep":4,"sort":52,"id":1663066,"subject_id":533027,"comment":21,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-08","name":"正真正銘の彼女","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":5,"sort":53,"id":1663067,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-15","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":6,"sort":54,"id":1663068,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-22","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":7,"sort":55,"id":1663069,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-29","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":8,"sort":56,"id":1663070,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-05","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":9,"sort":57,"id":1663071,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-12","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":10,"sort":58,"id":1663072,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-19","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":11,"sort":59,"id":1663073,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-26","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":12,"sort":60,"id":1663074,"subject_id":533027,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0}],"updat